00:26:37,870 --> 00:26:38,760
Thank you, Physician Fu.

577
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,760
Also, my home is far away.

578
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,350
I've come all this way with a nature call.

579
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:45,150
Can I use your restroom?

580
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,070
Of course.

581
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,280
It's in the backyard.

582
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:48,070
Do you need me to take you there?

583
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:48,870
Don't bother.

584
00:26:48,870 --> 00:26:49,830
I can go by myself.

585
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:51,000
Be my guest.

586
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:02,610
What trick are you playing?

587
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:12,480
Hulu.

588
00:27:13,310 --> 00:27:14,440
Why don't you go pack?

589
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:17,000
I don't really have anything to pack.

590
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:19,790
I just don't want to leave the chickens.

591
00:27:20,630 --> 00:27:21,410
I'd like to

592
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:24,040
fix their nest while I'm gone.

593
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:25,480
By the way, sir.

594
00:27:25,760 --> 00:27:26,590
What do you want from me?

595
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,350
Those people

596
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:30,720
are always hypocritically using us

597
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,590
like animals and exploiting us

598
00:27:33,390 --> 00:27:35,520
in the name of teaching us our skills.

599
00:27:36,390 --> 00:27:37,000
Hulu.

600
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:38,830
You're a gifted man.

601
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,200
Are you willing

602
00:27:40,280 --> 00:27:41,350
to spend your life here as a slave?

603
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:43,390
I...

604
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:46,660
Hulu.

605
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,040
Join us.

606
00:27:48,390 --> 00:27:49,960
We can give you what you want.

607
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,690
What can you give me?

608
00:27:53,150 --> 00:27:54,640
Understanding and dignity.

609
00:28:15,870 --> 00:28:16,240
Wait a minute.

610
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:18,720
You said you'd give me understanding and dignity,

611
00:28:18,870 --> 00:28:20,830
but you're all so secretive

612
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,520
and hide your identities.

613
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:23,070
You...

614
00:28:23,070 --> 00:28:23,480
So

615
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:25,390
how can I feel comfortable joining you?

616
00:28:25,870 --> 00:28:27,240
We want you to join us

617
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:29,790
because you're one of us

618
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:33,310
who's been ignored, discriminated against,

619
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:35,280
abused, and stepped on,

620
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:37,390
like the most insignificant

621
00:28:37,630 --> 00:28:39,240
and useless stone in the road.

622
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:43,800
What can a bunch of stones do?

623
00:28:44,230 --> 00:28:46,130
Stones can become a foundation

624
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:48,400
to form

625
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:50,790
or subvert a city.

626
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:53,920
What are you going to do?

627
00:28:54,230 --> 00:28:56,860
Xichuan should have belonged to people,

628
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:59,770
but those in power and rich merchants have taken over Xichuan

629
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:00,470
and reduced us,

630
00:29:00,470 --> 00:29:02,970
who have worked the hardest, to slaves.

631
00:29:03,470 --> 00:29:04,520
Are you happy with that?

632
00:29:05,230 --> 00:29:06,120
Are you willing?

633
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:07,780
No.

634
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:08,920
That's why

635
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,840
we'll take revenge on them

636
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:11,940
and drive them out.

637
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,600
So we can live here

638
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:14,940
with dignity.

639
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:21,360
Hulu.

640
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:23,260
When you complete the trials

641
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:24,840
and officially become a member of the Foundation,

642
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,960
you'll know who we are.

643
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:28,360
And by then,

644
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:31,640
you'll be able to do everything you want too.

645
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:33,930
What do you want me to do?

646
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:35,470
Hulu.

647
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:39,400
Do you find it interesting that an investigator

648
00:29:41,510 --> 00:29:42,880
becomes a murderer?

649
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:44,270
What...

650
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:45,840
What do you want to do?

651
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:02,070
If I were a murderer,

652
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:03,120
you'd already be dead.

653
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:07,880
You know something's wrong,

654
00:30:07,990 --> 00:30:09,030
but why would you still fall?

655
00:30:09,710 --> 00:30:12,270
Only by being prepared can we reduce our strength in time.

656
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:15,750
In haste, a man is bound to fall.

657
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,400
How's that?

658
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:25,640
Look at this.

659
00:30:28,990 --> 00:30:30,130
It's the light

660
00:30:30,290 --> 00:30:31,570
that spooked the horses.

661
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,270
This is it.

662
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:56,050
Why is there a sword formation here?

663
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:57,090
The other day,

664
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,160
the bell was ringing for no reason.

665
00:30:59,550 --> 00:31:00,420
We had looked into it for long

666
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:01,810
but couldn't find out the reason.

667
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:04,220
Then we invited an immortal

668
00:31:04,470 --> 00:31:05,540
to set up this sword formation

669
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:06,510
to ward off evil spirits.

670
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:07,730
Then

671
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,030
it never rang again.

672
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:10,920
Immortal?

673
00:31:11,470 --> 00:31:12,920
I don't think you're telling the truth.

674
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:16,270
It's not Eight Trigrams or Nine Palaces,

675
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:18,680
and it's not even an unpresentable Seven Luminaries.

676
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:20,470
The number's wrong.

677
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:22,860
The only thing it does

678
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:25,880
is totally reflect the sunlight

679
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:28,050
through this mirror

680
00:31:28,230 --> 00:31:29,550
in the alley where Hua Lei died.

681
00:31:37,230 --> 00:31:38,120
Is the immortal

682
00:31:38,710 --> 00:31:40,030
you?

683
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,600
This...

684
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:44,650
Everything I said is true.

685
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:45,400
And

686
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,510
I've reported all the expenses

687
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:50,200
for the Immortal to Lord's Mansion.

688
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:52,680
The Lord's Mansion paid the immortal directly.

689
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:53,750
You can ask them

690
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,430
about that, Young Mistress.

691
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:02,030
Where is the immortal now?

692
00:32:02,340 --> 00:32:05,940
[Glad for Your Coming]

693
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:09,680
Young Mistress.

694
00:32:10,470 --> 00:32:11,890
Is there an old madman here?

695
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:13,320
Yes, there is.

696
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,160
You mean the immortal?

697
00:32:15,990 --> 00:32:16,710
What immortal?

698
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:17,930
Call him out.

699
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:18,680
OK.

700
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:20,230
You don't need to.

701
00:32:21,360 --> 00:32:23,030
I expected a noble visitor today

702
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,640
by cauterizing a tortoiseshell

703
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:26,920
and observing its patterns on a whim,

704
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:29,270
but I did not expect

705
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,920
Young Mistress Xichuan to come personally.

706
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:33,840
This made me feel shameful.

707
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:35,690
Do you know

708
00:32:35,790 --> 00:32:37,170
why I've come to see you?

709
00:32:37,170 --> 00:32:37,920
[Fortune-telling]

710
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:40,230
What I did in the bell tower was nothing.

711
00:32:40,270 --> 00:32:42,270
It was a small token of my devotion

712
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,400
to the people of the city.

713
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,380
I lost ten years of my life

714
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:49,030
to exorcise the evil,

715
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,990
but I made the world peaceful,

716
00:32:51,230 --> 00:32:53,230
which fulfilled one of my wishes.

717
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,380
He is indeed a madman.

718
00:32:54,790 --> 00:32:55,160
Get him.

719
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,400
You talk a lot.

720
00:32:59,400 --> 00:32:59,880
I...

721
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:02,270
Why did you do this?

722
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,510
You didn't see this coming,

723
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:04,240
did you, old man?

724
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,070
Tell me.

725
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:06,960
Who ordered you to kill Hua Lei?

726
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:09,160
What do you mean?

727
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,880
You must be mistaken.

728
00:33:14,630 --> 00:33:15,280
Let him go.

729
00:33:15,630 --> 00:33:16,150
What's wrong?

730
00:33:16,590 --> 00:33:17,680
This bamboo slip

731
00:33:17,790 --> 00:33:20,200
indeed details a sword formation to exorcise evil spirits,

732
00:33:20,390 --> 00:33:22,520
exactly the same as the one on the bell tower.

733
00:33:22,810 --> 00:33:24,350
What do you know?

734
00:33:24,870 --> 00:33:26,760
This is our ancestral treasure.

735
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,760
How can you mortals

736
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,630
understand it?

737
00:33:31,150 --> 00:33:32,310
It's an ancient artifact,

738
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:34,890
but the wooden document recording the chapter on evil breaking

739
00:33:34,890 --> 00:33:35,680
has been switched,

740
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:38,160
so it's newer than the ones

741
00:33:38,390 --> 00:33:39,720
in the other chapters.

742
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:41,540
The rope does look like it's been switched.

743
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:42,480
It's new.

744
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:43,920
Give it to me.

745
00:33:47,630 --> 00:33:48,520
Little brat...

746
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:49,920
What do you mean?

747
00:33:50,350 --> 00:33:51,150
The other day,

748
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:53,760
the rope of my book suddenly broke.

749
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,310
My pupil suddenly became diligent

750
00:33:56,310 --> 00:33:58,000
and wanted to replace the string for me,

751
00:33:58,280 --> 00:34:01,000
but I didn't realize he was so bold

752
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,550
as to dare tamper with the contents.

753
00:34:04,550 --> 00:34:05,110
This is really...

754
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:07,310
Where is your disciple now?

755
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:08,630
He went out yesterday at noon

756
00:34:08,630 --> 00:34:10,360
and hasn't returned yet.

757
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:12,880
When he comes back, I'll kill him.

758
00:34:13,270 --> 00:34:14,230
Isn't that the time

759
00:34:14,230 --> 00:34:15,920
we chased after Cui?

760
00:34:17,010 --> 00:34:17,750
Right.

761
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:19,500
Sir.

762
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,770
How do you know about

763
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:22,670
the clock tower being haunted?

764
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:23,400
I...

765
00:34:24,590 --> 00:34:26,690
I heard it from my apprentice.

766
00:34:28,070 --> 00:34:30,400
Another bullied esne.

767
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:33,320
Then it's no coincidence.

768
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:36,880
Madam.

769
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:38,700
Something's happened.

770
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:41,070
The Jibei Chamber of Commerce is picking on us again?

771
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:42,960
Not us.

772
00:34:43,270 --> 00:34:45,220
It's the clinic.

773
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,320
Hold on.

774
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:58,190
Stick out your tongue.

775
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,520
The tongue coat is yellow.

776
00:35:04,630 --> 00:35:06,710
Someone tampered with my prescription

777
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:07,670
and replaced it with a laxative.

778
00:35:08,270 --> 00:35:09,710
Who did it?

779
00:35:10,270 --> 00:35:11,000
It was that little pharmacist.

780
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:12,150
That little pharmacist

781
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,840
gave us all the medicine we took.

782
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,800
Hulu?

783
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:20,220
[Moral and Artistic Stature]

784
00:35:20,750 --> 00:35:21,360
Hulu's gone.

785
00:35:23,070 --> 00:35:24,710
The patient's family has surrounded the place

786
00:35:25,190 --> 00:35:27,230
and said we're killing people.

787
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,040
Let's go out.

788
00:35:35,270 --> 00:35:37,110
- Hand over the killer! - They refused to hand him over!

789
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:41,270
- Come out. - Come out.

790
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:42,630
Everybody, just calm down.

791
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:43,960
Come out.

792
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:45,190
Come out.

793
00:35:45,190 --> 00:35:46,290
Come out.

794
00:35:46,290 --> 00:35:47,220
Calm down.

795
00:35:51,550 --> 00:35:52,440
Regarding this matter,

796
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,820
I believe Physician Fu will give you an explanation.

797
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:55,360
An explanation?

798
00:35:55,750 --> 00:35:56,920
What can you explain?

799
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:58,630
They are just killing people.

800
00:35:59,110 --> 00:35:59,840
I heard earlier

801
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,750
that your doctor at the clinic

802
00:36:02,150 --> 00:36:02,920
is a murderer.

803
00:36:03,190 --> 00:36:03,590
Now,

804
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,070
they have really started killing people.

805
00:36:05,270 --> 00:36:05,920
Nonsense.

806
00:36:06,270 --> 00:36:07,590
All of us from Ma Gang

807
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:08,960
come to this clinic when we're injured.

808
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:10,840
If Physician Fu was really a quack,

809
00:36:11,270 --> 00:36:13,040
we'd have demolished the clinic.

810
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:14,440
Then he's up to no good.

811
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:14,800
That's right.

812
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,480
Physician Fu has been

813
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,970
with Fang Zhiyuan for the past few days,

814
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,520
so who knows if they're in cahoots?

815
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:20,000
Right.

816
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:20,740
Are you all in this together

817
00:36:20,740 --> 00:36:21,360
and trying to kill us?

818
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,150
Who's yelling?

819
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:25,670
Come out.

820
00:36:25,670 --> 00:36:27,780
[Wenfu Hall]

821
00:36:31,590 --> 00:36:32,110
Look.

822
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:33,960
Lord's Mansion is with them.

823
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,710
They won't leave us alive.

824
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,150
Get in.

825
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:39,820
Feel guilty?

826
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:42,840
Feel guilty?

827
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:43,630
Why are you running away?

828
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,550
What's going on here?

829
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:50,190
Fu Sheng.

830
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:51,880
Who have you offended?

831
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:54,440
Someone is trying to set us up.

832
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:56,400
It must be organized by those behind the scenes.

833
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:58,480
They're doing this to show they're anxious.

834
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,280
Put out a bounty notice,

835
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,180
