836
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:02,800
and find out who's behind it.

837
00:37:03,070 --> 00:37:03,980
Who's wanted?

838
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,820
People are calling us names.

839
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:08,320
Do you know who's behind this?

840
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:10,840
Make Hulu wanted.

841
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:19,880
Be careful.

842
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,000
Steward Sun, someone wants to see you.

843
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,480
Physician Fu.

844
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:32,840
Have a seat.

845
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:41,960
I heard

846
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:45,070
one of your physicians lost the medicine chest,

847
00:37:47,590 --> 00:37:48,360
so would you like me

848
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,050
to retrieve your work essentials

849
00:37:50,050 --> 00:37:50,770
for you?

850
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:54,150
The city lord has issued a bounty notice

851
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:55,750
and closed Xichuan.

852
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:57,750
There's nowhere for that thief to run.

853
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:01,360
Then why are you here today?

854
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:03,360
Because of Hua Lei's death.

855
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,840
I have some idea about the cause of his death.

856
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,050
As far as I know,

857
00:38:08,150 --> 00:38:09,450
Hua Lei, the unlucky jerk,

858
00:38:09,450 --> 00:38:10,970
was killed by a man called Night Owl,

859
00:38:10,970 --> 00:38:11,580
wasn't he?

860
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,220
So what are you still investigating?

861
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:15,580
Night Owl was just being used too.

862
00:38:16,190 --> 00:38:18,490
Someone rigged that alley,

863
00:38:18,750 --> 00:38:20,130
making Hua Lei fall off his horse

864
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:21,860
